      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. but if I do the honey thing, how much should I actually put on? like do i need a thick layer to make sure it stays sealed, or just a little? and should i wrap it tight with a bandage to keep the pressure on so it stops oozing? i really just want to get this sorted so i can go back to what i was doing.",
